[{"Id": 1012160, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "It is narrated from Jabir that after the passing away of the Messenger of Allah (s) two persons from among the companions of Prophet came to her and asked: How are you, O daughter of Prophet? She replied: First of all you testify my statement, did you hear the Messenger of Allah (s) say: “Fatima is a part of me; one who causes distress to her has caused distress to me.” Both replied: “Yes, by Allah, we heard this from him.” Fatima raised her hands to the heavens and said…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Jabir se riwaayat hai keh jab Rasool-e-Khuda (s) is duniya se chal-basey to woh dono ghaasib Bibi Fatema (s) ke paas aaye aur kaha aap kaisi ho ay Rasool ki dukhtar? Bibi ne farmaya: pehle aap dono meri baat ki gawahi do, keh kya tum logo’n ne Allah ke Rasool (s) se yeh nahi soona, “Fatema mere jigar ka tukda hai jis ne usko (Fatima ko) gazab-naak kiya goya us ne mujhe gazab-naak kiya.: Un dono ne kaha: “Ba-khuda ham ne un se yeh soona tha.” Us waqt Bibi ne apne haatho’n ko aasmaan ki taraf baland kar ke kaha…", "UrduDescription": null, "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8":